  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Labelling tobacco products and e-cigarettes if there’s a no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How tobacco products and e-cigarettes will be regulated if the UK leaves the EU with no deal.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

